Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,(松本菜奈实)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.46,0:01:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,大家，今后请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,去大阪三年\N说话完全成关西方言了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,和之前相比真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我最擅长和他做事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我去洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,三年前，我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在和他一起的公司里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,松本，来一下\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这个订单怎么回事？\N比上个月的金额低这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,客户的仓库里面\N好像还剩下很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你是傻吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还坐在办公室里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,还不赶快去找出路\N卖掉库存
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,快一点动起来\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么看起来关系那么好？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在交往吗？\N没有，我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,菜奈实，一起去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,吃的好干净啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真好，真好，很符合你的口味吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来杯咖啡，咖啡\N好的，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,能带你来这里，真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有点小贵\N所以要和大家保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们知道我带你来这里吃饭\N就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好小一杯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,意式咖啡都这样吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,菜奈实的更大吧？\N有多少罩杯？胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那很糟糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,性骚扰也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\N真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我，告诉了当时的部长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,梅田的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,梅田被派遣到大阪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,过了不久，我就结婚辞职了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那之后，过了3年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,（被厌恶的男人抱紧）\N（想死的感觉帮他射精）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是我，喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那个，不能拒绝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,老公，你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,菜奈实，好久不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他好像喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,先让他躺下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那去卧室吧\N这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉鞋子，鞋子\N到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这边？\N不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,再来，再来\N到这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,老公，你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到他喝酒这么容易醉\N真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我老公给你添烦了，抱歉\N不会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这样说来，你们都结婚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,礼金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很久之前就结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系，没关系\N拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,现在没电车了\N让我住这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我去准备被子\N我睡在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,老公，没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,要喝水吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,老公，在洗澡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我借用一下浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你的胸部又大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这又是性骚扰吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘记东西了\N忘了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,很重要的\N可以的话，我帮你拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己找更快\N打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可能没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我突然从大阪回来\N你没想到吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,之前都是你向部长告发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,才害得我被派遣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我是部长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,错的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌\N请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗？\N请不要摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不要遮掩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这么大的胸部\N好恶心，放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,请放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不想我插进去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,其实很期待吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这么大的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,想被大家盯着看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好讨厌，滚开，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,再一起开心一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,请放开我\N在说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你做我的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一起开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚结婚2年吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要摸我\N在发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他也会这样摸吗？\N像这样，吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,请放开我\N还是好久没做过了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我会帮你爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部这样很舒服吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的下面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要摸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,想要了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手\N只是被摸了很舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这里，这样吗？\N请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,请放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，这个味道让我忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:20:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,让我好好品尝一下\N不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜欢吧？\N这样感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，好害羞，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,让我好好品尝一下\N不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，好恶心\N不要舔了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这个不需要了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.83,0:22:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N手指很简单的插进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔一下吗？\N不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,其实想要了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.09,0:23:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.56,0:23:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.23,0:23:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.80,0:24:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢被我这样套弄吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.84,0:24:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.81,0:24:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.72,0:24:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊\N住手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.42,0:24:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.81,0:25:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.09,0:26:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,含到喉咙深处\N太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.46,0:27:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.06,0:27:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,想你这样帮我夹住
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.51,0:27:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,想要这样的刺激吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.35,0:27:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都会幻想这样吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.36,0:27:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这样比较舒服吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.07,0:27:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,都夹住了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.97,0:28:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.81,0:28:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,再一起开心一下吧\N住手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.46,0:28:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来是这边\N这边
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.69,0:28:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.77,0:28:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，不可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.67,0:28:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,下面那么湿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.37,0:28:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.98,0:28:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.28,0:28:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.26,0:28:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢这样吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.06,0:28:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.70,0:29:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.97,0:29:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去了\N不行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.98,0:29:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,龟头\N不行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.38,0:29:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那么可爱的脸蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.69,0:29:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看一下插入瞬间你的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.34,0:29:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.74,0:29:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以\N慢慢的插到里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.55,0:29:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢的\N不行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.37,0:30:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.27,0:30:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.48,0:30:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.48,0:30:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.77,0:30:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.14,0:30:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,想我全部插满吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.44,0:30:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.75,0:30:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.59,0:31:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不行，停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.74,0:31:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.51,0:31:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好恶心，屁股翘起来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.82,0:31:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.63,0:31:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.64,0:31:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.88,0:31:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.71,0:32:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.45,0:32:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.83,0:32:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以，停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.81,0:32:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,去了，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.55,0:32:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.14,0:33:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.41,0:33:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.94,0:33:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.39,0:33:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.36,0:33:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.76,0:34:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很咸吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.36,0:34:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,想我插进去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.77,0:35:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.30,0:35:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.37,0:35:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,阴茎，想我插进去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.54,0:35:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.92,0:36:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.14,0:36:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服\N不行
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.08,0:36:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我要射了，要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.50,0:37:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.40,0:37:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是周日
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.27,0:37:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他还要上班\N你很寂寞吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.48,0:37:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,直的好差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.36,0:38:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.06,0:38:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,之前一起工作的时候\N我就光看你的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.37,0:39:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,会把事情说出去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.07,0:39:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不会告诉松尾吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.55,0:39:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会说吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.29,0:39:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,被厌恶的男人插满骚穴
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.46,0:39:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个烂人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.10,0:39:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是希望你把拍的照片\N全部删掉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.77,0:39:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.22,0:39:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,转一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.23,0:40:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,很期待吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.31,0:40:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看一下胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.29,0:41:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,手拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.93,0:41:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，下面
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.45,0:42:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,手拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.56,0:42:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,转一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.14,0:42:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是T字裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.05,0:42:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,穿着内裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.02,0:42:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,很期待吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.33,0:42:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是你让我穿的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.43,0:42:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我没想到你真的穿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.24,0:43:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是简单说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.12,0:43:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你就忘不了了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.59,0:43:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,总说不喜欢不喜欢\N其实那么敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.35,0:43:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.68,0:43:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,发出声音了吧？\N不是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.52,0:43:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下，请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.99,0:43:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那你来这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.27,0:44:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这么硬了\N怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.44,0:44:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很期待吧？\N不是
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.11,0:44:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.45,0:44:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,被我摸了，知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.89,0:44:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前就超喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.39,0:44:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部都被揉捏了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.72,0:45:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好柔软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.23,0:45:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,全拿起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.53,0:45:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.47,0:45:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可以再好好玩一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.28,0:45:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,想我怎么摸？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.09,0:45:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这么柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.19,0:45:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,看到这样的胸部\N就有干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.36,0:45:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.70,0:45:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,想我删掉吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.81,0:45:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不会告诉你老公的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.28,0:45:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.73,0:46:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,松尾知道这个事情怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.06,0:46:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,会辞职吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.23,0:46:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.51,0:46:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那个我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.64,0:46:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的很兴奋吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.72,0:46:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.92,0:46:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,从外面可能会被看到
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.04,0:46:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,翘起来
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.38,0:46:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真好，好有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.29,0:47:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.85,0:47:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是闻一下味道
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.36,0:47:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.69,0:47:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.09,0:47:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很兴奋吧？这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.26,0:47:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.42,0:48:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊，这个胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.04,0:48:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.38,0:48:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗？\N请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.02,0:48:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧？\N不是
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.83,0:49:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,想我舔吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.80,0:49:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.68,0:49:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,站好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.75,0:49:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看一下你淫荡的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.40,0:49:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,从上面开始舔
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.63,0:50:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,用舌尖
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.17,0:50:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舔一下
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.21,0:50:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好敷衍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.91,0:50:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是想舔其他的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.33,0:51:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,想看这里吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.14,0:51:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.12,0:51:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,来含住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.31,0:52:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,想我插进去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.55,0:52:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,美味吗？\N不要客气
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.71,0:53:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？继续
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.10,0:53:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.23,0:54:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦，再含住到深处
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.77,0:54:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,都含住到深处了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.22,0:54:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,舔一下龟头
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.73,0:55:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那里好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.31,0:55:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,来夹住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.79,0:56:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.76,0:56:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没做过吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.30,0:56:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.05,0:57:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,都夹住了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.66,0:58:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.09,0:58:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,再继续，再来
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.63,0:59:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.78,0:59:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服，是的，继续
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.96,0:59:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.04,0:59:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.34,0:59:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,来含住
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.99,0:59:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.31,1:00:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那样，继续
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.65,1:00:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，继续
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.97,1:00:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,再激烈一点
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.52,1:01:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，再慢慢轻一点
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.23,1:01:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉很好
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.37,1:01:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，继续，就是那样
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.84,1:01:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.60,1:01:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.31,1:02:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还有呢\N停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.55,1:02:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,到最后为止\N全舔干净
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.32,1:02:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就那样发出声音
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.90,1:02:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,含住到喉咙深处
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.25,1:02:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.03,1:02:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.38,1:03:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.54,1:04:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,给我解开
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.78,1:04:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,躲开
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.99,1:04:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.29,1:04:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.93,1:04:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头周围很舒服吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.34,1:04:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我\N那么敏感
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.74,1:04:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个房间吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.68,1:04:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢这样的性骚扰吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.38,1:05:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.65,1:05:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很敏感吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.69,1:05:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,特别舒服吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.69,1:05:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手\N只是这样摸，乳头就这么硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.97,1:05:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.18,1:05:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,说请住手的同时\N反应那么好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.61,1:05:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.40,1:06:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.94,1:06:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,再好好爽一下\N不要客气
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.11,1:06:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，不行
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.35,1:06:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.62,1:06:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看过吧？\N不行
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.33,1:06:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，不行
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.78,1:07:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.68,1:07:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可以再发出声音
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.42,1:07:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.53,1:07:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头这么硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.16,1:08:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这边很舒服吧？\N不行
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.93,1:08:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不行\N乳头很舒服吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.14,1:08:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看一下摩擦的地方\N很兴奋了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.62,1:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.04,1:09:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.25,1:09:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.34,1:09:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N胸部已经很舒服了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.78,1:09:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这边\N不行
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.38,1:09:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.46,1:10:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.73,1:10:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,发出可爱的声音
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.70,1:10:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我会再帮你好好爽的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.87,1:10:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.68,1:10:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不行
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.50,1:10:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,槽糕
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.84,1:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不行
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.14,1:10:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\N不行
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.45,1:11:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.49,1:11:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,从内裤上面
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.52,1:11:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样\N不行
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.82,1:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.80,1:11:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,去了，不行，不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.57,1:11:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.04,1:11:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不行
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.09,1:12:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了吗？
